# Migrations Directory Security

## This directory should be protected from web access

### Apache (.htaccess)
```apache
<Files "*">
    Require all denied
</Files>
```

### Nginx 
Add to your nginx configuration:
```nginx
location /migrations {
    deny all;
    return 404;
}
```

### Flask Production
In production, ensure this directory is outside the web root or properly protected.
